USING DOCKER

Run the following docker command:
    docker run -p 5000:5000 -p 80:8000  smartapi


MANUALLY RUNNING THE ENDPOINT:

If no docker is available and there is python3 installed on the machine run: 

from the src folder run:
    pip install -r requirements

then tp start the server
    python -m flask run --host=0.0.0.0


THE UI

the UI will run on http://localhost:5000/ui

for manual run, select local from the dropdown the localhost address,
for the docker run, select the address http://172.17.0.2:5000/ from the dropdown.
